  "title": "Spicy Savory Korean Rice Bowl",
  "description": "A spicy and savory Korean dish featuring mixed grain rice, topped with a cheese-pull and a variety of spicy ingredients, perfect for a hangover cure.",
  "cuisine": "Korean",
